  "body": "Fixes #1999\n\n## Summary\n\n- Add `solve.resource-diagnostics.lib.mjs` to capture CPU load, CPU count, memory, process RSS, and full filesystem usage with `fs.statfsSync('/')`.\n- Record resource snapshots at solve start, after clone, after AI execution, before `safeExit`, and before/after AI restart iterations.\n- Parse resource markers in the session monitor so Docker completion messages can still show full container filesystem usage when post-exit Docker inspection cannot provide `containerFilesystemAfterBytes`.\n- Include outside-process CPU/memory/disk telemetry in Telegram bot heartbeat logs.\n- Compile the issue evidence, screenshot, timeline, root-cause analysis, and references in `docs/case-studies/issue-1999/`.\n\n## Reproduction\n\nThe issue screenshot shows the Docker `Disk usage` section with `Container filesystem size` only reporting `On start: 52 KB`; no completion value is present. The regression test recreates that state by giving the monitor a Docker start size, no Docker completion size, and final solve resource markers in the log. The expected completion block now includes `On completion: 7.0 GB` from the `solve_exit` marker.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `npm run lint`\n- `npm test` - all 296 selected test files passed after merging `origin/main`\n- `node tests/test-issue-1999-resource-diagnostics.mjs`\n- `node tests/test-issue-1999-session-monitor-disk-fallback.mjs`\n- `node tests/test-issue-1927-bot-lifecycle.mjs`\n- `npx prettier --check docs/case-studies/issue-1999/README.md .changeset/issue-1999-resource-diagnostics.md src/solve.resource-diagnostics.lib.mjs tests/test-issue-1999-resource-diagnostics.mjs tests/test-issue-1999-session-monitor-disk-fallback.mjs`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Case Study\n\n- Analysis: `docs/case-studies/issue-1999/README.md`\n- Screenshot evidence: `docs/case-studies/issue-1999/assets/issue-1999-screenshot.png`\n- Captured issue/PR metadata: `docs/case-studies/issue-1999/*.json`\n\n## References Used\n\n- Docker CLI `docker inspect --size`: https://docs.docker.com/reference/cli/docker/inspect/\n- Docker Engine API size fields: https://docs.docker.com/reference/api/engine/version/v1.43/\n- Node.js `fs.statfsSync`: https://nodejs.org/api/fs.html\n",
